en_855390_0	Brigadier S.M.S.P.B Samarakoon of Gajaba Regiment (GR) assumed office as the new Director of Veteran Affairs on Monday (30) at his office in the Army Headquarters at Sri Jayewardenepura.
en_855390_1	The newly-appointed Director left his signature in an official document amid religious observances.
en_855390_2	Staff officers of the Directorate, Officers and Other Ranks were present at the occasion.
